13: Well, whatever happens, even if you say "I won't listen!" to my words of advice as we talk to each other, even if you people each work the land by yourself, as you have been intending to--wherever you work, at least  work well! Cultivate the soil properly, and try to gain your food and drink, so that you will not be inferior to others.[8] \
