71: Yep, rice-harvest time has come. Tomorrow I plan to go start trying to reap. Since the wild pigs are eating away at it. \
72: Kheh-ki, have you managed to try harvesting yet? \
73: Yes, I plan to try to harvest. My field has just begun to ripen a little, too, now. Tomorrow I'll go reap,[43]  I guess. \
74: Jali, what about you?\
75: Well, mine is being harvested.  Even today.\
76: I see. Well, how many bushels [44]  have you gotten this year?\
